     * as an explicit JSON `null` (â†’ SQL NULL locally, â†’ server column NULLed on flush). Only the
     * `?? null` columns are clearable ([`clearable_columns`] â€” `isbn`/covers here); a column both
     * set and cleared, or a non-clearable name, is rejected and nothing is staged.
